AI Copy Agent — Product Brief
Objective
Build an AI Copywriting Agent specialized in Direct-Response Conversion Copy.
The agent will generate high-converting marketing copy by combining:
Customer research


Product information


Direct-response frameworks


Large databases of proven examples


Page-type specific system prompts


The system must generate copy that is extremely relevant, persuasive, and conversion-focused.
The model used for copy reasoning must be:
Claude Opus (latest version)
This model will be responsible for all copy generation and research synthesis.

Core Concept
The AI Copy Agent works by combining three data sources:
1. Customer Research
Used to make copy feel real, emotional, and relevant.
Examples:
reviews


testimonials


support tickets


survey answers


forum posts


interviews


objections



2. Product Information
Used to build the problem → mechanism → solution narrative.
Examples:
product description


ingredients/components


mechanism explanation


benefits


proof


testimonials



3. Direct-Response Knowledge Database
The AI is trained on a database containing:
proven advertorials


winning offer pages


upsell pages


listicles


conversion frameworks


copywriting books


persuasion guides


CRO frameworks


This database provides patterns, structures, and persuasion techniques.

Copy Generation Workflow
The AI agent follows this process:
Step 1 — Understand Customer Psychology
Extract from research:
core pain points


emotional frustrations


fears


desired outcomes


objections


language customers use



Step 2 — Understand the Product
Analyze:
what problem it solves


how it works


unique mechanism


key benefits


credibility



Step 3 — Select Copy Type
The user selects the type of copy to generate.
Each type has:
its own system prompt


its own guidelines


its own example database



Step 4 — Generate Copy
The AI combines:
research insights


product knowledge


persuasion frameworks


proven examples


To generate structured, high-converting copy.

