Prompt System Architecture
The AI should operate using layered prompts.

Layer 1 — Global System Prompt
Defines the AI's role:
Example:
Direct Response Copywriter + CRO Specialist
Responsibilities:
conversion optimization


persuasion frameworks


customer psychology



Layer 2 — Page Type Prompt
Each copy type has its own system prompt.
Examples:
Advertorial prompt
 Offer page prompt
 Upsell prompt
 Listicle prompt
 Thank you page prompt
These prompts define:
tone


structure


persuasion strategy


narrative flow



Layer 3 — Guidelines
Each page type also has writing rules.
Example guidelines:
Advertorial:
editorial tone


curiosity gaps


discovery narrative


Offer page:
clarity


strong benefits


proof stacking


Upsell:
fast persuasion


minimal friction



Layer 4 — Example Database
Each page type has a library of examples.
Examples include:
high-performing funnels


winning sales pages


advertorial case studies


The AI references these examples to understand:
structure


persuasion patterns


messaging style



