System Architecture Summary
The AI Copy Agent includes:
1 — Research Analyzer
Extracts insights from customer research.

2 — Product Intelligence Module
Understands product mechanism and benefits.

3 — Prompt Engine
Selects the correct prompt based on copy type.

4 — Example Library
Provides proven structures and persuasion patterns.

5 — Copy Generator
Produces structured conversion copy.

